1.HMI Buttons
    a. toggle buttons (Pause, Test Mode, Unload, Step Mode)
        setOn() - toggle button on
        setOff() - toggle button off

    b.  normal buttons
        LockButton
            setLocked()
            setUnlocked()

2. Misc
    EngMode
        setOn() - show eng mode message
        setOff() - hide eng mode message

    PLCState
        setState(state)
            0 = The Machine is Idle
            1 = The Machine is Initializing
            2 = The Machine is Ready
            3 = The Machine Works
            4 = The Machine is Paused
            5 = The Machine is Halted

3. DIO
    DI
        setActive()
        setInactive()
    DO
        setActive()
        setInactive()
